%% Data Flow Diagram - Notebooks (Workbench Images)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Cluster Admin
    participant RhodsOp as rhods-operator
    participant K8sAPI as OpenShift API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant NotebookCtrl as odh-notebook-controller
    participant Kubelet as kubelet
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BuildCtrl as OpenShift Build Controller
    participant GitHub as github.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant IntReg as Internal Registry<br/>5000/TCP HTTPS

    Note over RhodsOp,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Workbench Image Deployment

    RhodsOp->>K8sAPI: Apply kustomize manifests<br/>(ImageStreams + ConfigMaps)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>RhodsOp: Resources created

    User->>Dashboard: Browse available workbenches
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: List ImageStreams<br/>(label: opendatahub.io/notebook-image=true)<br/>Auth: Bearer token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: ImageStream metadata<br/>(names, annotations, tags)
    Dashboard-->>User: Display workbench options

    User->>Dashboard: Create workbench<br/>(select image + config)
    Dashboard->>NotebookCtrl: Create Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer token, TLS 1.2+
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Resolve ImageStream tag<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Image digest reference
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod + HTTPRoute<br/>+ inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Pod scheduled

    Kubelet->>Registry: Pull workbench image (N-1)<br/>Auth: Pull secret, TLS 1.2+
    Registry-->>Kubelet: Container image layers
    Kubelet->>Quay: Pull workbench image (N-2 to N-6)<br/>Auth: Pull secret, TLS 1.2+
    Quay-->>Kubelet: Container image layers

    Note over BuildCtrl,IntReg: Flow 2: RStudio BuildConfig Execution

    BuildCtrl->>GitHub: Clone source code<br/>HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    GitHub-->>BuildCtrl: Source archive
    BuildCtrl->>Registry: Pull base image<br/>Auth: Pull secret, TLS 1.2+
    Registry-->>BuildCtrl: Base image layers
    Note over BuildCtrl: Build RStudio image<br/>(uses rhel-subscription-secret<br/>for package installation)
    BuildCtrl->>IntReg: Push built image<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    IntReg-->>BuildCtrl: Image pushed
